Package: coadministr
Type: Package
Title: Trial simulator for coadministration design
Version: 1.0
Date: 2021-04-07
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Mark",
           family = "Mark",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "mark@example.com")
Description: Simulates data and trial progression for rct evaluting adverse
    event rates associated with coadministration of covid19 and flu vaccine 
    relative to covid19 and placebo. Multiple interim analyses, constructed
    so that decisions can be made on the basis of inferiority and also
    non-inferiority.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Biarch: true
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.4.0)
Imports: 
    coadministr.stanc,
    rstan,
    data.table
